===Pronunciation===
ראשׁית / rê'shîyth / ray-sheeth'

===Etymology===
From the same as [[ראשׁ]] {{HH|7218}}; 

===Noun===
'''ראשׁית'''

# the first, in place, time, order or rank (specifically a firstfruit): - [[beginning]], chief (-est), first (-fruits, part, time), principal thing.

